  "description": "<p>CANDIDATE</p><p>1. MUST HOLD ANY DIPLOMA OR DEGREE IN ENGINEERING IN A RECOGNISED</p><p>UNIVERSITY/BOARD</p><p>2. MUST HAVE A MINIMUM OF 5 YEARS OF EXPERIENCE IN THE CONSTRUCTION SECTOR</p><p>3. MUST BE FLUENT IN ENGLISH.</p><p>4. SHOULD COOPERATE FOR OVERTIME WORKING IF NECESSARY</p><p>5. SHOULD FOLLOW SUPERIOR'S INSTRUCTION TIME TO TIME</p><p>6. SHOULD BE FAMILIAR WITH SINGAPORE ROAD ROOTS</p><p>7. SHOULD HAVE CLASS 3 DRIVING LICENCE</p><p>8. SHOULD OBEY THE COMPANY RULES AND REGUL</p><p>9 SHOULD BE ABLE TO HANDLE THE SITE INDEPENDENTLY</p><p>10 LEISON TO THE MANAGEMENT AND SITE COORDINATION</p><p>11. SAFETY COORDINATOR COURSE IN SINGAPORE BCA WILL BE AN ADDED ADVANTAGE</p>",
